desc:
You transform into an amoebic form composed of highly acidic and poisonous alchemical jelly. While in this form:
* you are immune to ácido and daño de veneno and to the envenenado and aturdido conditions;
* you have resistance to no mágico fuego, perforante, and daño cortante;
* you can’t speak, cast spells, use items or weapons, or manipulate objects;
* your gear melds into your body and reappears when the spell ends;
* you don't need to breathe;
* your Velocidad is 20 pies;
* your size doesn’t change, but you can move through and between obstructions as if you were two size categories smaller; and
* you gain the following action: **ataque cuerpo a cuerpo con arma:** spellcasting ability modifier + competencia bonus para impactar, range 5 pies., un objetivo; **Hit:** 4d6 ácido or daño de veneno (your choice), and the objetivo debe realizar a successful tirada de salvación de Constitución or be envenenado until the start of your next turn.
